---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---
<Base
  title="Car Rental Dubai Marina 2026 — From AED 35/day"
  description="Compare car rentals in Dubai Marina. Delivery to your building. Economy from AED 35/day. Perfect for tourists and digital nomads."
>
<div class="bg-navy text-white py-12 px-4 text-center">
  <div class="text-sm text-blue-300 mb-2">📍 Dubai Marina</div>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-black mb-3">Car Rental Dubai Marina — From AED 35/day</h1>
  <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Compare car rental companies delivering to Dubai Marina, JLT, and Marina Walk. Free delivery to your building.</p>
  <a href="/get-quotes?ref=dubai-marina" class="bg-yellow-400 text-navy px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-black hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-colors inline-block">Get Marina Car Rental Quotes →</a>
</div>
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow p-4 mb-10">
    <iframe src="https://www.discovercars.com/engine/rent-a-car/iframe?a_aid=YOUR_AFFILIATE_ID&location=Dubai+Marina&lang=en&curr=AED" width="100%" height="420" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" title="Dubai Marina Car Rental — Compare Prices"></iframe>
  </div>
  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy">Car Rental in Dubai Marina</h2>
    <p>Dubai Marina is one of Dubai's most popular residential and tourist areas, home to over 120 towers with a permanent population of 50,000+. Car rental operators offer free delivery to Marina buildings, with economy cars starting from AED 35/day.</p>
    <p>The Marina is well-connected by tram and metro, but a car gives you access to attractions like Mall of the Emirates, Dubai Parks, and the desert excursions that public transport cannot reach. Most tourists staying in JBR or Marina rent for 3–7 days.</p>
    <p>Parking is available in most Marina buildings for AED 0–20/day. Street parking via the RTA mParking app costs AED 2–4/hour during peak times.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 text-center">
    <a href="/car-rentals" class="text-brand font-semibold hover:underline">← Back to all car rental areas</a>
  </div>
</div>
</Base>
